<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 06:09:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军决定在以色列北部重新开放高中，但令家长们不相信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-lets-galilee-high-schools-reopen-parents-are-unconvinced/0000018e-9612-d9a4-a7bf-de5b53930000</link><description>以色列军队鼓励以色列北部被疏散的地区重新开放两所高中，但学生往返学校行程的模糊性迫使家长陷入临时教育框架造成的困境</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-lets-galilee-high-schools-reopen-parents-are-unconvinced/0000018e-9612-d9a4-a7bf-de5b53930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对战后加沙的“多国部队”宣传只不过是一厢情愿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-multinational-force-pitch-for-postwar-gaza-is-little-more-than-wishful-thinking/0000018e-9614-dd2f-a7cf-d73d4a060000</link><description>随着战后加沙谈判变得更加紧迫，战后由哪个军事实体重建加沙地带的问题变得更加复杂——美国不愿意，巴勒斯坦权力机构不能，而任何愿意派遣军队的阿拉伯国家都将被指责与以色列勾结。职业</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-multinational-force-pitch-for-postwar-gaza-is-little-more-than-wishful-thinking/0000018e-9614-dd2f-a7cf-d73d4a060000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在以色列与哈马斯人质谈判中向内塔尼亚胡施加压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/protesters-up-the-pressure-on-netanyahu-amid-israel-hamas-hostage-negotiations/0000018e-9620-da88-afff-f73d569e0000</link><description>当前的示威浪潮自战争开始以来首次对内塔尼亚胡构成挑战 ■ 哈马斯允许巴勒斯坦居民自由返回加沙北部的要求是以色列方面人质谈判的争论焦点</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/protesters-up-the-pressure-on-netanyahu-amid-israel-hamas-hostage-negotiations/0000018e-9620-da88-afff-f73d569e0000</guid></item><item><title>东耶路撒冷定居点获得数百万美元修建运动场 - 巴勒斯坦邻国却没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-settlement-gets-millions-for-sports-field-palestinian-neighbors-go-without/0000018e-95f1-d229-adae-95f302860000</link><description>东耶路撒冷的犹太飞地诺夫锡安 (Nof Zion) 的 90 个家庭将获得一个市政府资助的运动场，而周围的 Jebel Mukkaber 社区的 30,000 名居民却缺乏这个运动场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-settlement-gets-millions-for-sports-field-palestinian-neighbors-go-without/0000018e-95f1-d229-adae-95f302860000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列国防军已离开希法医院；以色列士兵在加沙南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-live/netanyahus-surgery-successful-three-wounded-in-southern-israel-stabbing-attack/0000018e-9762-d9a4-a7bf-df7bcabb0000</link><description>哈马斯领导人亲属在以色列被捕 ■ 伊拉克亲伊朗民兵称其向埃拉特发射无人机 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告以色列国防军已离开希法医院 ■ 以色列国防军称士兵在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 02:58:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-live/netanyahus-surgery-successful-three-wounded-in-southern-israel-stabbing-attack/0000018e-9762-d9a4-a7bf-df7bcabb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列机构报告自 10 月 7 日以来网络攻击大幅增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-agency-reports-significant-surge-in-cyberattacks-since-oct-7/0000018e-95dc-d9a4-a7bf-dddd37b30000</link><description>以色列国家网络局的报告发现，去年报告的超过 13,000 起针对民用目标的网络攻击中，有 68% 发生在 10 月 7 日之后</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 00:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-agency-reports-significant-surge-in-cyberattacks-since-oct-7/0000018e-95dc-d9a4-a7bf-dddd37b30000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在该国南部发生持刀袭击事件受伤；袭击者被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-in-countrys-south-assailant-shot-dead/0000018e-967b-de60-a1be-97fb916c0000</link><description>警方确认袭击者为来自约旦河西岸多拉村的 19 岁穆明·阿尔哈利勒 (Mumeen Al-Khalil) ■ 一名高级警官称，他在南部城镇甘亚夫内 (Gan Yavne) 购物中心旁的一家咖啡馆里袭击了三名年轻人</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 22:41:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-in-countrys-south-assailant-shot-dead/0000018e-967b-de60-a1be-97fb916c0000</guid></item><item><title>一些人质家属的反内塔尼亚胡声明揭示了内部纠纷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-declaration-by-some-hostages-families-reveals-internal-disputes/0000018e-95ae-dd2f-a7cf-d7bf6a540000</link><description>经过数周的克制后，一些家庭呼吁驱逐内塔尼亚胡，因为与哈马斯的谈判明显陷入僵局。与此同时，其他家庭则认为此举过于对抗，并明确表示不同意</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 19:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-declaration-by-some-hostages-families-reveals-internal-disputes/0000018e-95ae-dd2f-a7cf-d7bf6a540000</guid></item><item><title>数万人在耶路撒冷集会，要求内塔尼亚胡下台；抗议者封锁道路、纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/hostages-dont-get-to-take-recess-but-somehow-they-can/0000018e-9582-dd2f-a7cf-d7bb8dbc0000</link><description>耶路撒冷的大规模集会和组织者计划在以色列议会外搭建的帐篷城是自 10 月 7 日以来的首次此类行动。“我不相信我必须与政府官员斗争才能获得我兄弟返回家园的权利，”人质的姐姐说</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 19:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/hostages-dont-get-to-take-recess-but-somehow-they-can/0000018e-9582-dd2f-a7cf-d7bb8dbc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长阻止内塔尼亚胡绕过最高法院停止犹太基金的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/ag-blocks-netanyahus-efforts-to-bypass-top-court-ruling-stopping-yeshiva-funds/0000018e-94fc-da88-afff-f5fd540b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理组建了一个特别小组，负责寻找方法规避高等法院冻结其学生拒绝参军的犹太学院预算的命令。总检察长迄今为止阻止了这一举措，称所有选择都将违反该命令</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/ag-blocks-netanyahus-efforts-to-bypass-top-court-ruling-stopping-yeshiva-funds/0000018e-94fc-da88-afff-f5fd540b0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不需要非犹太人的恩惠”：内塔尼亚胡政府是一个辛辣的讽刺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-31/ty-article/.highlight/we-dont-need-favors-from-the-goyim-netanyahus-government-is-a-bitter-irony/0000018e-9566-dd2f-a7cf-d77f48f90000</link><description>有些承诺以前被认为是国家与其公民之间契约的基础——床上安全；以明确的战略和道德界限来应对可怕的袭击。但这对于本届政府来说是完全陌生的</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:36:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-31/ty-article/.highlight/we-dont-need-favors-from-the-goyim-netanyahus-government-is-a-bitter-irony/0000018e-9566-dd2f-a7cf-d77f48f90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 177 天：以色列代表团抵达开罗进行人质释放会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-177-israeli-delegation-lands-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-talks/0000018e-9570-da88-afff-f57db4860000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达开罗参加人质释放谈判 ■ 据报道，以色列在黎巴嫩南部杀害了真主党高级官员 ■ 高级保守党议员声称英国收到了以色列在加沙违反国际法的法律建议 ■ 周四在约旦河西岸向以色列车辆开火的巴勒斯坦人■ 贝都因以色列男子在贝尔谢巴刺伤士兵后被枪杀 ■ 战争结束 177 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-177-israeli-delegation-lands-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-talks/0000018e-9570-da88-afff-f57db4860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院推翻了对阻挡警察水炮的著名反内塔尼亚胡活动人士的定罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/court-overturns-conviction-of-anti-netanyahu-activist-who-blocked-police-water-cannon/0000018e-94df-da88-afff-f5ffe32b0000</link><description>反对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议运动领导人戈南·本·伊扎克承认，他故意干扰水炮的使用，因为警察即将以危及示威者的方式使用水炮。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 14:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/court-overturns-conviction-of-anti-netanyahu-activist-who-blocked-police-water-cannon/0000018e-94df-da88-afff-f5ffe32b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙设立了“杀戮区”。任何闯入其中的人都会被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-created-kill-zones-in-gaza-anyone-who-crosses-into-them-is-shot/0000018e-946c-d4de-afee-f46da9ee0000</link><description>以色列军队称，自加沙战争爆发以来，已有 9000 名恐怖分子被打死。然而，国防官员和士兵告诉国土报，这些人往往是平民，他们唯一的罪行就是越过以色列国防军划定的无形界限</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 13:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-created-kill-zones-in-gaza-anyone-who-crosses-into-them-is-shot/0000018e-946c-d4de-afee-f46da9ee0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷最后的绿地之一的争夺战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-over-one-of-the-last-undeveloped-hills-in-jerusalem/0000018e-9423-d4de-afee-f42f67a00000</link><description>吉瓦特哈塔纳赫 (Givat Hatanach) 计划建设一座新的酒店综合体，这是该市仅存的几座未开发的山丘之一。居民和专家警告当地自然环境和历史城堡受到破坏，而英国政府则严重关注其对现场苏格兰教堂的影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 11:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-over-one-of-the-last-undeveloped-hills-in-jerusalem/0000018e-9423-d4de-afee-f42f67a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行行长表示，加沙战争期间未来的国防支出需要更加明确</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/israels-central-bank-chief-says-more-clarity-on-defense-spending-needed-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-943a-d229-adae-95fb05260000</link><description>以色列立法者批准在 2024 年国家预算中增加数十亿谢克尔，以资助以色列对抗哈马斯的战争，因为战争目标的不确定性和加沙计划的“后天”迫在眉睫</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 11:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/israels-central-bank-chief-says-more-clarity-on-defense-spending-needed-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-943a-d229-adae-95fb05260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军军官在以色列南部发生持刀袭击事件中受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-stabbed-in-suspected-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-9372-d4de-afee-f37f57970000</link><description>这名 28 岁的袭击者是贝都因市拉哈特的居民，在刺伤后被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-stabbed-in-suspected-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-9372-d4de-afee-f37f57970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端正统派领导人表示内塔尼亚胡的联盟不会因正统军队征兵而崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/as-draft-exemption-expires-ultra-orthodox-leaders-signal-coalition-wont-collapse/0000018e-90dc-d229-adae-91df8bea0000</link><description>尽管以色列极端正统派社区感到愤怒，但联盟领导人并不认为犹太学院学生服兵役的政治危机会对依赖正统政党的总理内塔尼亚胡的联盟构成直接威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 02:43:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/as-draft-exemption-expires-ultra-orthodox-leaders-signal-coalition-wont-collapse/0000018e-90dc-d229-adae-91df8bea0000</guid></item><item><title>为期四天的集会在耶路撒冷拉开帷幕，反内塔尼亚胡抗议运动面临考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-govt-protest-to-peak-in-jerusalem-ahead-of-knesset-recess/0000018e-90f5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfdccd30000</link><description>以色列针对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议运动计划在耶路撒冷议会外建立一个帐篷城，以疏导公众的愤怒，以确保议会春季休会前有强劲的投票率</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 02:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-govt-protest-to-peak-in-jerusalem-ahead-of-knesset-recess/0000018e-90f5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfdccd30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部发生刺伤袭击，三名以色列人受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-live/police-clash-with-anti-govt-protesters-16-arrested-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9214-d8cd-a9ce-977660560000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的疝气手术成功，总理“状况良好” ■ 以色列国防军表示，可疑飞机进入以色列并在南部城市埃拉特附近坠毁；没有人员伤亡报道 ■ 数千人在议会外抗议，呼吁提前选举 ■ 以色列代表团抵达开罗就停火、释放人质协议进行谈判</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 01:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-live/police-clash-with-anti-govt-protesters-16-arrested-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9214-d8cd-a9ce-977660560000</guid></item></channel></rss>